      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院因反对王室改革而解散反对党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宪法法院裁定该国最大的反对党修改严格的王室诽谤法，违反了选举规则，随后下令解散该党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯任命辛瓦尔为政治领袖，打破停火希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯任命 10 月 7 日袭击事件的主要策划者叶海亚·辛瓦尔为其新政治领导人，这是对达成加沙停火协议的多边努力的最新打击。]]></description>
